@startuml
title FreshFood Observability (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

node "FreshFood Backend\nFastAPI :8001" as Backend
node "Prometheus :9090" as Prom
node "Grafana :3001" as Grafana
node "Promtail" as Promtail
node "Loki :3100" as Loki
folder "backend/logs/*.log" as LogFiles

Backend --> Prom : /metrics\n(freshfood_http_*, freshfood_scan_events_total)
LogFiles --> Promtail : tail files
Promtail --> Loki : push logs

Grafana --> Prom : query metrics datasource
Grafana --> Loki : query logs datasource

note right of Prom
target scrape:
host.docker.internal:8001
path: /metrics
end note

note right of LogFiles
As-is gap:
Promtail da cau hinh doc log file,\nnhung app chua thay config ghi log file ro rang.
end note

@enduml
